Title: real-time-checks: systemd compatibility
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1631470435
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0p12

The previous approach of the RTC feature did not work with
systemd. This werk changes the way real time data
transmission is triggered, such that they work with systemd.
